*.html

# Option 2: Keep everything except cache (CURRENT CHOICE)
# We commit feeds and resources for GitHub Pages
# but ignore the HTML cache
!data/
!data/feeds/
!data/feeds/v1/
!data/feeds/v1/*.json
!data/feeds/v2/
